    <item>
      <title>沃伦·巴菲特的美国银行抛售潮即将迈向关键里程碑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/warren-buffett-s-bofa-selling-spree-edges-toward-key-milestone</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过十几轮抛售，沃伦·巴菲特 (Warren Buffett) 持有的美国银行 (Bank of America Corp.) 股份已降至关键监管门槛的边缘，届时他将不再需要迅速向公众通报其交易情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/warren-buffett-s-bofa-selling-spree-edges-toward-key-milestone</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 23:04:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平推出大规模刺激计划 旨在结束中国经济放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/xi-s-big-stimulus-week-aims-to-draw-a-line-under-china-slowdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几个月来，尽管股市下跌、物价下跌、中国各地的不满情绪不断增长，但国家主席习近平似乎并未因经济增长放缓而感到不安。本周，他表明自己不愿再忍受任何痛苦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/xi-s-big-stimulus-week-aims-to-draw-a-line-under-china-slowdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
